You have decided that you would like to visit some different areas around the country. You now have several options of places to visit. 
The place you choose may benefit you politically as well as benefit you personally.

<<link [[1. I want to visit the agricultural district | Visit Agricultural District]]>> <<set $playerstress -= 1>><</link>>
